  PracticeFeature,partials/practice/feature.html,practice workspace shell,app
  ReviewQuiz,partials/review/quiz.html,review flip card answer controls and voice selector,app|speech|lookup|terms
  ReviewList,partials/review/review-list.html,browsed word trail,review-list
  ResultScreen,partials/review/result.html,review completion screen,app
  LookupPopup,partials/review/lookup-popup.html,example word meaning popup,lookup
  SettingScreen,partials/setting/setting.html,daily word count form,setting-ui|settings
  FavoritesScreen,partials/favorites/favorites.html,favorite word list,favorites-ui|favorites
