m.data[6]{name,path,desc,deps}:
  pte_vocab,pte_vocab.json,570 vocabulary items with word partOfSpeech definition example wordFamily and collocations,vocab
  favorites,Firestore users/{uid}/favorites,signed-in user's saved vocabulary,firebase|auth
  quizAttempts,Firestore users/{uid}/quizAttempts/{date},daily vocabulary exam answer and score records,firebase|auth
  examAttempts,Firestore users/{uid}/examAttempts/{date},daily cloze exam answer and score records,firebase|auth
  settings,localStorage pte.dailyWordCount|pte.clozeEndlessMode,daily deck size and cloze endless-mode preference,settings
  lookupCache,sessionStorage pte.lookup.*,cached online example word meanings,lookup
m.tool[3]{name,path,desc,deps}:
  Jest tests,test/package.json,Jest 30 jsdom ES-module test command,index.test.js|exam.test.js|terms.test.js
  run-tests,test/run-tests.bat,Windows test launcher,test/package.json
  start-server,start-server.bat,untracked local Python HTTP server launcher,Python
